        <l n="c">ntisalārggaṁ bāradeṁbantuṭaṇa kaḷa<choice><orig>s</orig><reg>ś</reg></choice>a nirbbāṇam appanegaṁ mā</l>
        <l n="d">ḍisidaṁ vkrōkti-vācaspati pa<choice><orig>ṁ</orig><reg>pa</reg></choice>ti-hitar ācāryyan ī śaṁ<choice><orig>kh</orig><reg>k</reg></choice>arāryyaṁ<g type="ddanda">.</g><g type="SpiralI"></g></l>
